---
import Navbar from '../../components/navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import tokiai3 from '../../assets/tokiai3.png';
import tokiai4 from '../../assets/tokiai4.png';
import tokiai5 from '../../assets/tokiai5.png';

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return [
    {params: {id: '1'}},
    {params: {id: '2'}},
    {params: {id: '3'}},
    {params: {id: '4'}},
    {params: {id: '5'}},
    {params: {id: '6'}},
    {params: {id: '7'}},
    {params: {id: '8'}},
    {params: {id: '9'}},
  ];
}
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="da">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Nordic Essense - TOKI</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navbar />

    <main class="work-detail">
      <div class="work-detail-container">
        <!-- Back Button -->
        <a href="/" class="back-button">← Back to Home</a>

        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="work-header">
          <h1 class="work-main-title">NORDIC ESSENSE</h1>
          <p class="work-subtitle">PREMIUM PACKAGING REDESIGN FOR A NATURAL COSMETICS BRAND</p>

          <div class="work-meta">
            <div class="meta-item">
              <p class="meta-label">Client</p>
              <p class="meta-value">Nordic Essense — Premium Natural Cosmetics</p>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <p class="meta-label">Location</p>
              <p class="meta-value">Copenhagen, Denmark</p>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <p class="meta-label">Timeline</p>
              <p class="meta-value">6 months</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Grid -->
        <div class="work-content-grid">
          <!-- Left: Images -->
          <div class="work-images">
            <img src={tokiai3.src} alt="Nordic Essense packaging" class="work-image-large" />
            <div class="work-image-row">
              <img src={tokiai4.src} alt="Product detail 1" class="work-image-small" />
              <img src={tokiai5.src} alt="Product detail 2" class="work-image-small" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Text Content -->
          <div class="work-text">
            <div class="text-section">
              <h3 class="text-section-title">THE BRIEF</h3>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                Nordic Essense, a fast-growing Scandinavian skincare brand focused on natural ingredients and minimalist aesthetics, was ready to evolve.
              </p>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                They approached TOKI to create packaging that would reflect their premium positioning, while elevating the brand's international appeal.
              </p>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                Their goals were clear:<br />
                • Shift perception from "natural and affordable" to "premium Scandinavian design"<br />
                • Use eco-friendly, tactile materials<br />
                • Strengthen visual recognition both on shelf and online<br />
                • Simplify packaging processes to reduce costs while improving quality and consistency.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-section">
              <h3 class="text-section-title">THE OUTCOME</h3>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                • Aesthetic clarity drives perceived brand value (survey-based)
              </p>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                • 12% cost reduction per unit through smarter material sourcing
              </p>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                • Winner of the Sustainable Design Award in Beauty & Personal Care
              </p>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                • 38% growth in online sales and improved unboxing experience
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-section">
              <h3 class="text-section-title">KEY LEARNINGS</h3>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                • Aesthetic clarity drives commercial performance
              </p>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                • Insight-led design generates expensive packaging solutions
              </p>
              <p class="text-section-content">
                • Sustainability and scalability must evolve in parallel, not as trade-offs
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background-color: #FAF2E7;
    color: #333;
  }

  .work-detail {
    background-color: #FAF2E7;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
  }

  .work-detail-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .back-button {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    background-color: #DDBA4E;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid #000;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .back-button:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .work-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .work-main-title {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .work-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .work-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
    min-width: 80px;
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #666;
  }

  .work-content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .work-images {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .work-image-large {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .work-image-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .work-image-small {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .work-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .text-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .text-section-title {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #333;
  }

  .text-section-content {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1vw, 0.9rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .work-content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .work-detail {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .work-detail-container {
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .work-header {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .meta-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    .work-content-grid {
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .work-detail-container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .work-image-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
